{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BKqVKAiSm2tuNL9cAUJNki","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Cinis Terminal Context\n     2→Read this before every task.\n     3→\n     4→## Brand\n     5→- Coal #211A14 — background\n     6→- Hot Pool #FF6644 — PRIMARY accent, all interactive elements\n     7→- Ember #E8321A — RESERVED: delete, overdue, urgent ONLY\n     8→- Ash #F0EAD6 — primary text\n     9→- Char #3E3228 — cards, inputs, surfaces\n    10→- Gold #FFB800 — Pro/subscription only\n    11→- Green #4CAF50 — completed/success only\n    12→- Body: Figtree. Numbers/wordmark: Sora.\n    13→- Wordmark: CINIS, Sora 600, 0.16em, uppercase\n    14→- Tagline: \"Where start meets finished.\"\n    15→- NEVER: Cormorant Garamond, $9.99, \"FocusBuddy\"\n    16→\n    17→## Layout\n    18→- paddingBottom: 80px on all scrollable content (Voice FAB clearance)\n    19→- Content padding: 12px 14px on all tabs\n    20→- Sidebar: width 106px, padding 12px 8px\n    21→- Cards: background Char, border rgba(240,234,214,0.08), radius 12px\n    22→- Inputs: radius 8px, background Char\n    23→\n    24→## DB Column Names (exact)\n    25→profiles: id, full_name, persona_blend (text[]), baseline_profile (text),\n    26→  rolling_memory_summary, subscription_status, ai_interactions_today,\n    27→  current_streak, longest_streak, total_xp, theme_id, push_subscription,\n    28→  push_notifications_enabled, morning_time, midday_time, evening_time,\n    29→  checkin_times (array), onboarding_complete, birthday\n    30→\n    31→tasks: id, user_id, title, completed, archived, scheduled_for,\n    32→  completed_at, due_time, rollover_count, notes, sort_order,\n    33→  starred (boolean), task_type (text), estimated_minutes (integer)\n    34→\n    35→bills: id, user_id, name, amount (numeric), due_day, frequency,\n    36→  category, autopay, notes, auto_task\n    37→\n    38→journal_entries: id, user_id, content, ai_response, mood, created_at\n    39→\n    40→progress_snapshots: id, user_id, snapshot_date, tasks_completed,\n    41→  tasks_added, tasks_rolled, focus_minutes, journal_entries, ai_summary\n    42→\n    43→habits: id, user_id, name, frequency, habit_type ('build'/'break')\n    44→habit_completions: id, habit_id, user_id, completed_at\n    45→\n    46→## Do Not Touch\n    47→- lib/memoryCompression.js\n    48→- lib/rateLimit.js\n    49→- pages/api/stripe/webhook.js\n    50→- lib/supabase.js auth config\n    51→\n    52→## Auth Pattern\n    53→- Plain createClient from @supabase/supabase-js\n    54→- onAuthStateChange fires only on INITIAL_SESSION and SIGNED_IN\n    55→- No getSession(). No callback.js. No @supabase/ssr.\n    56→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ca4d693b-e152-4f30-9b86-91ce85d7189b","uuid":"ab219c80-2756-4f83-a479-ffd6e7b9bc5f","timestamp":"2026-03-26T16:46:45.360Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ryanjohnson/Documents/focusbuddy-app/docs/TERMINAL_CONTEXT.md","content":"# Cinis Terminal Context\nRead this before every task.\n\n## Brand\n- Coal #211A14 — background\n- Hot Pool #FF6644 — PRIMARY accent, all interactive elements\n- Ember #E8321A — RESERVED: delete, overdue, urgent ONLY\n- Ash #F0EAD6 — primary text\n- Char #3E3228 — cards, inputs, surfaces\n- Gold #FFB800 — Pro/subscription only\n- Green #4CAF50 — completed/success only\n- Body: Figtree. Numbers/wordmark: Sora.\n- Wordmark: CINIS, Sora 600, 0.16em, uppercase\n- Tagline: \"Where start meets finished.\"\n- NEVER: Cormorant Garamond, $9.99, \"FocusBuddy\"\n\n## Layout\n- paddingBottom: 80px on all scrollable content (Voice FAB clearance)\n- Content padding: 12px 14px on all tabs\n- Sidebar: width 106px, padding 12px 8px\n- Cards: background Char, border rgba(240,234,214,0.08), radius 12px\n- Inputs: radius 8px, background Char\n\n## DB Column Names (exact)\nprofiles: id, full_name, persona_blend (text[]), baseline_profile (text),\n  rolling_memory_summary, subscription_status, ai_interactions_today,\n  current_streak, longest_streak, total_xp, theme_id, push_subscription,\n  push_notifications_enabled, morning_time, midday_time, evening_time,\n  checkin_times (array), onboarding_complete, birthday\n\ntasks: id, user_id, title, completed, archived, scheduled_for,\n  completed_at, due_time, rollover_count, notes, sort_order,\n  starred (boolean), task_type (text), estimated_minutes (integer)\n\nbills: id, user_id, name, amount (numeric), due_day, frequency,\n  category, autopay, notes, auto_task\n\njournal_entries: id, user_id, content, ai_response, mood, created_at\n\nprogress_snapshots: id, user_id, snapshot_date, tasks_completed,\n  tasks_added, tasks_rolled, focus_minutes, journal_entries, ai_summary\n\nhabits: id, user_id, name, frequency, habit_type ('build'/'break')\nhabit_completions: id, habit_id, user_id, completed_at\n\n## Do Not Touch\n- lib/memoryCompression.js\n- lib/rateLimit.js\n- pages/api/stripe/webhook.js\n- lib/supabase.js auth config\n\n## Auth Pattern\n- Plain createClient from @supabase/supabase-js\n- onAuthStateChange fires only on INITIAL_SESSION and SIGNED_IN\n- No getSession(). No callback.js. No @supabase/ssr.\n","numLines":56,"startLine":1,"totalLines":56}}}
